Loews Hotels









LOEWS HOTELS

Loews Hotels

Loews Hotels owns and/or operates 24 hotels and resorts in the United States and Canada. Located in major city centers and resort destinations from coast to coast, the Loews portfolio features one-of-a-kind properties that go beyond Four Diamond standards to delight guests with exciting, approachable and local travel experiences.





BY THE NUMBERS





1. Excludes the Loews Don CeSar Hotel, which was sold in Q1 2017.


 



