Diamond Offshore









DIAMOND OFFSHORE


Diamond Offshore Drilling, Inc. provides contract drilling services to the global energy industry.  Diamond is a leader in deepwater drilling and has a strong and liquid balance sheet. The company’s fleet consists of 24 offshore drilling rigs including 19 semisubmersibles, four dynamically positioned drillships and one jack-up.





BY THE NUMBERS





1. Includes active and non-active rigs as of February 6, 2017.


 



