Loews Corporation is a holding company. Its principal subsidiaries are CNA Financial Corporation, Boardwalk Pipeline Partners LP, Diamond Offshore Drilling, Inc., Loews Hotels. Bulova Corporation, a former subsidiary, was bought by Citizen Watch Company in January 2008.

On April 11, 2017,… MoreLoews Corporation is a holding company. Its principal subsidiaries are CNA Financial Corporation, Boardwalk Pipeline Partners LP, Diamond Offshore Drilling, Inc., Loews Hotels. Bulova Corporation, a former subsidiary, was bought by Citizen Watch Company in January 2008.

On April 11, 2017, Loews Corporation agreed to acquire Consolidated Container Company from Bain Capital Private Equity for approximately $1.2 bn.
Loews Corporation is a holding company. Its principal subsidiaries are CNA Financial Corporation, Boardwalk Pipeline Partners LP, Diamond Offshore Drilling, Inc., Loews Hotels. Bulova Corporation, a former subsidiary, was bought by Citizen Watch Company in January 2008.

•Loews sold its HighMount… MoreLoews Corporation is a holding company. Its principal subsidiaries are CNA Financial Corporation, Boardwalk Pipeline Partners LP, Diamond Offshore Drilling, Inc., Loews Hotels. Bulova Corporation, a former subsidiary, was bought by Citizen Watch Company in January 2008.

•Loews sold its HighMount subsidiary to EnerVest in September, 2014.

The IT Department for Loews Corporation is based at the company's headquarters in New York, NY. Loews Corporation is comprised of several business divisions each with a vice president in charge of IT operations and services. The CTO of Loews Hotels oversees shared IT services for Loews Corporation and Loews Hotels. At the corporate headquarters are directors and managers for both Loews Corporation and Loews Hotels who oversee several IT divisions including Data Storage, Applications Systems, and web development.

The department for Boardwalk Pipeline Partners is independent of the parent company. Based in Owensboro, KY, the subsidiary is led by a CIO who oversees all IT operations and services. Her office is located in Houston, TX. Also supporting the department are managers who oversee Network Operations and Security.

CNA FINANCIAL CORPORATION IS MAINTAINED AS A SEPARATE PROFILE WITHIN THE DATABASE.

DIAMOND OFFSHORE DRILLING IS MAINTAINED AS A SEPARATE PROFILE WITHIN THE DATABASE.
 





