Loews Corporation Presents at 39th Annual NYU International Hospitality Industry Investment Conference 2017, Jun-04-2017 through Jun-06-2017
Jun 1 17
Loews Corporation Presents at 39th Annual NYU International Hospitality Industry Investment Conference 2017, Jun-04-2017 through Jun-06-2017. Venue: New York, United States. Presentation Date & Speakers: Jun-05-2017, Jonathan M. Tisch, Co-Chairman, Chairman of Loews Hotels and Chief Executive Officer of Loews Hotels. Jun-06-2017, Laura K. Cushing, Vice President of Human Resources.


Loews Corporation Declares Quarterly Dividend on Common Stock, Payable June 13, 2017
May 9 17
Loews Corporation announced the declaration of the company's quarterly dividend of $0.0625 per share of common stock, payable June 13, 2017 to shareholders of record as of the close of business on May 31, 2017.


Loews Corporation Seeks Acquisitions 
May 3 17
Loews Corporation (NYSE:L) stated that the acquisition of Consolidated Container Company LLC, will add new industry to Loews' already diverse portfolio of businesses and provide foundation for expansion through organic growth and bolt-on acquisitions.



